725647f-b.title: Queens: 78th Street - Woodside Avenue
725647f-b.text:
78th Street, north from Woodside Avenue. The photograph
shows the course of the street before it was cut through to
connect with Broadway. W. P. A. construction work can be
seen just east of this intersection.
P. L. Sperr  November 5, 1936
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1, 2
